form.official-title: To designate the facility of the United States Postal Service located at 100 Mathe Avenue in Interlachen, Florida, as the Robert H. Jenkins, Jr. Post Office.

section.header: Robert H. Jenkins, Jr. Post Office

subsection.text: The facility of the United States Postal Service located at 100 Mathe Avenue in Interlachen, Florida, shall be known and designated as the Robert H. Jenkins, Jr. Post Office.

Any reference in a law, map, regulation, document, paper, or other record of the United States to the facility referred to in subsection (a) shall be deemed to be a reference to the Robert H. Jenkins, Jr. Post Office.

attestation-group.attestation-date: Passed the House of Representatives November 15, 2017.
